title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – May 4 2022

description:
Tyrus from Fox News hangs with C&B, talks about his new book. Fed raises interest rates. Trigger warning! Clay and Buck respond to Joy Behar's sex strike threat, segue into segment on dating. Clay and Buck talk history. Caller asks if Uncle Buck could manage looking after the Travis kids. VIP email on Behar.
